<emphasis bold="true" box="[667,682,1998,2023]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">n</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[700,726,1998,2023]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">sp</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
resemble those of 
<taxonomicName box="[962,1108,1998,2023]" class="Arachnida" family="Anyphaenidae" genus="Xiruana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="23" pageNumber="224" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gracilipes">
<emphasis box="[962,1108,1998,2023]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">X. gracilipes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[1172,1274,1998,2023]" class="Arachnida" family="Anyphaenidae" genus="Xiruana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="23" pageNumber="224" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cocha" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[1172,1274,1998,2023]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">X. cocha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1284,1352,1998,2023]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224" rank="species">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1284,1299,1998,2023]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">n</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1318,1344,1998,2023]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">sp</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
by the epigynal plate with a triangular posterior border, but differs by the lack of a furrow along the anterior border and by the seminal receptacles inserted near the spermathecae (
